title: Ang Laga De Song - Ram-leela ft. Deepika & Ranveer HD 1080p
description:
Ang Laga De Song - Ram-leela ft. Deepika & Ranveer HD 1080p {GreatPalash}

Witness the sizzling chemistry between Ranveer Singh & Deepika Padukone in "Ang Laga De" from Ram-leela. The song is sung by Aditi Paul & Shail Hada.

Music: Sanjay Leela Bhansali
Lyrics: Siddharth - Garima

Ang lagaa de re

Ram ratan dhan, lagan magan mann,

Tu hawaa de ise

Jalaa de re sang jalaa de re
Mohe ang laga de re
Main toh teri joganiya

Eros International & Bhansali Productions presents 'Ram-leela' a Sanjay Leela Bhansali film featuring Ranveer Singh & Deepika Padukone. The film is produced by Kishore Lulla & Sanjay Leela Bhansali & is all set to release in theaters on 15th November, 2013.
